`patched('add-notify-customer')` returns `false` when replaying a workflow that was started before the patch was introduced. The `else` branch preserves the exact original sequence — `chargeCard` → `sleep(10s)` → `shipOrder` — so replay succeeds without non-determinism errors. No `notified:` line is written to `/workspace/notify.log` for these executions.

**New executions (`order-new-*`)**  
